column5: Well me and Justin hit the BOQ for 2 days fishing was tough with the full moon but managed a few nice fish...lots of open water all over up there but lots of good areas to fish safe ice ..if you heading up shoot me a PM were to fish ...and thanks to the people that Pmed me were to fish ...all though we didnt fish those areas all the info was great . ;D Thanks Fishmasters Ultimate Charters
